.org/resource/Surrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pools\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"gyms\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"her target\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harvey never made it but, just two years since turning professional, will run for Britain in Paris in themarathon.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999505072443656, \"rank\": 4.932947168158467e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999967849362, \"rank\": 3.2150929062956113e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Harvey\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"themarathon\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am proud to say I was last at school sports day,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school sports day\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully inspiration to any children reading that you do not have to be brilliant at everything - just enjoy sport, find your passion and the rest will follow.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hopefully inspiration\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"any children\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"your passion\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At university, I joined the rowing club, mainly for the Wednesday night parties!\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"university\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"the rowing club\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wednesday night parties\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so lucky to have had a very normal experience of school, university, and a career.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very normal experience\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"university\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sport at a young age can be a high-pressure environment.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 1199, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-pressure environment\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I got the partying out of my system and now have no sense of missing out when I am training hard and getting early nights.\\\"\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the partying\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1286}, {\"ngram\": \"my system\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"no sense\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"early nights\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel incredibly lucky to be going to the Olympics this year...\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I never dreamed or let myself believe it could happen Rose Harvey Had it not been for the pandemic and her redundancy, in all likelihood she would never have become an Olympian at the age of 31.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.562102698231591e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rose Harvey\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"her redundancy\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"all likelihood\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just two years ago, I was a full-time lawyer in the City, so I feel incredibly lucky to be going to theOlympicsthis year,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full-time lawyer\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsthis year\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never dreamed or let myself believe it could happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Surrey selection was the initial target, but her first race of note was the 2021 Cheshire Marathon, which she completed in 2hr 30min 59sec and earned selection for England's half-marathon team.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"score\": 0.8823865605444755, \"rank\": 0.13326047336179064, \"text\": \"Surrey\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Surrey\"}, {\"begin\": 2012, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9901360695660476, \"rank\": 0.009473718215519407, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the initial target\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"her first race\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"note\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2021 Cheshire Marathon\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"2hr 30min 59sec\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From there, her \\\"lockdown project snowballed\\\".\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her \\\"lockdown project\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She ran the Seville Marathon, impressing enough to get a DM message on Instagram from Puma and the offer of a professional contract, allowing her to resign from her relatively new legal job.\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2147, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dungeon_Master\", \"score\": 0.9081942307235028, \"rank\": 0.06804569756170806, \"text\": \"DM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dungeon_Master\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dungeon_Master\"}, {\"begin\": 2161, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0259043019630903e-27, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Seville Marathon\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"Puma\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"the offer\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional contract\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"her relatively new legal job\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions 10 great gift ideas that earn you Avios At the 2022 London Marathon, she was the fastest British finisher and set a PB at last year's Chicago Marathon of 2:23.21, the fifth best by a British runner of all time.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2413, \"end\": 2429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999651873220291, \"rank\": 1.2831007391294794e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999651873220291, \"rank\": 1.2831007391294794e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proud\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"Enhanced Games Sports quiz\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"100 hard questions\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible year\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slam Track decision\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"2025 ambitions\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"10 great gift ideas\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"Avios\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 London Marathon\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"a PB\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's Chicago Marathon\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"2:23.21\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her London run was all the more impressive as she was hit by a car in training the week before, which she kept secret from everyone.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999985707291, \"rank\": 9.503198936327334e-10, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a car\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harvey said: \\\"It was a tough week with a very bruised left knee, but it ended happily.\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Harvey\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough week\", \"from\": 2852, \"to\": 2864}, {\"ngram\": \"a very bruised left knee\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know I have had a very different journey to most other professional athletes, but I do also believe my law career gave me a lot of transferrable skills in becoming a professional athlete.\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very different journey\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"most other professional athletes\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"my law career\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"transferrable skills\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional athlete\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to be able to keep your head under pressure, have perspective and a good amount of resilience.\\\"\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your head\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3149}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3164}, {\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"a good amount\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harvey has been gearing up for these Games with altitude training in the French Pyrenees.\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3291, \"end\": 3306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyrenees\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French Pyrenees\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyrenees\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyrenees\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Harvey\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"altitude training\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She admitted: \\\"If someone said to me four years ago I would be preparing for the Olympics, I would have told them they were mad.\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3334}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But there are many ways to attain most goals if you are happy to put in the work, take the sacrifices and commit.\\\"\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"most goals\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3484}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3520}, {\"ngram\": \"the sacrifices\", \"from\": 3527, \"to\": 3541}]}, {\"sentenc